            Meet Our Board of Directors
    

Highly-respected in their professions and experts in their fields, this group of folks help us maintain a vision of health care that is more comprehensive, more affordable, and more patient-focused.













            Capital District Physicians’ Health Plan, Inc. (CDPHP®)
    






            CDPHP Universal Benefits,® Inc. (CDPHP UBI)
    






            Capital District Physicians’ Healthcare Network, Inc. (CDPHN)
    






            Founding CDPHP Board of Directors
    









            Capital District Physicians’ Health Plan, Inc. (CDPHP®)	
    
We are a not-for-profit, physician-directed health plan licensed under Article 44 of the Public Health Law of New York State. We offer a variety of health maintenance organization (HMO) plans and state and federally subsidized government programs.

