            CDPHP Universal Benefits,® Inc. (CDPHP UBI)
    
CDPHP UBI is a not-for-profit corporation licensed under Article 43 of the New York State Insurance Law. Products marketed through CDPHP UBI include exclusive provider organization (EPO) and preferred provider organization (PPO) plans.

